courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, C1, C2, Lower-Division C Elective, Upper-Division C, D1, Area D Elective, Lower-Division E, and F. USCP requirement can be satisfied by some (but not all) courses within GE categories: C1, Upper-Division C, D1, D2, Upper-Division D, or E.
